Extract a structured profile from the operator's raw text below.

=== CV / RESUME ===
{cv_text}

=== GIT ACTIVITY ===
{git_log_text}

=== SLACK / COMMS ===
{slack_text}

Return STRICT JSON with exactly these keys:
{{
  "skills": [lowercase canonical tech skills, e.g. "python", "react", "ml"],
  "work_style": [8 floats in 0..1 for: collaboration, autonomy, structure, innovation, pace, communication, risk_tolerance, remote_preference],
  "motivation_vector": [8 floats in 0..1 for: impact, growth, compensation, stability, creativity, recognition, autonomy, mission_alignment],
  "career_goals": [short phrases the operator wants next, e.g. "move to ML", "lead role"]
}}

Infer each dimension from behavioral signals in the text (async/remote working, leadership/mentoring, research vs delivery, shipping cadence, stability vs novelty). Output JSON ONLY.
